const svg = $('#frob-svg'), out = $('#frob-out');
// three root positions
const R = [[160,130],[310,80],[460,130]];
const LABELS = ['α₁','α₂','α₃'];
const PERMS = {
  a: {name:'3-cycle',    perm:[1,2,0], factorisation:'f̄(x) irreducible of degree 3'},
  b: {name:'transposition', perm:[1,0,2], factorisation:'f̄(x) = (deg 2) · (deg 1)'},
  c: {name:'identity',   perm:[0,1,2], factorisation:'f̄(x) = (x−r₁)(x−r₂)(x−r₃), three linear'},
};
let key = 'a';
function render(){
  while(svg.firstChild) svg.removeChild(svg.firstChild);
  for(let i=0;i<3;i++) drawNode(svg, R[i][0], R[i][1], LABELS[i], {r:22, stroke:'var(--blue)'});
  const P = PERMS[key];
  for(let i=0;i<3;i++){
    const j = P.perm[i];
    if(i===j){
      // loop
      const [x,y] = R[i];
      ensureArrow(svg,'frob-fix','var(--green)');
      const d = `M ${x-12} ${y-26} C ${x-40} ${y-70}, ${x+40} ${y-70}, ${x+12} ${y-26}`;
      svg.appendChild(SVG('path',{d, fill:'none', stroke:'var(--green)','stroke-width':1.6,'marker-end':'url(#frob-fix)'}));
    } else {
      const curve = (i<j)?32:-32;
      drawArrow(svg, R[i], R[j], {
        color:'var(--yellow)', curve, markerId:'frob-'+key+'-'+i,
        pad1:24, pad2:26, width:1.8
      });
    }
  }
  // caption + shape
  const shape = cycleShapeFromPerm(P.perm);
  const t = SVG('text',{x:310,y:210,'text-anchor':'middle','font-size':13,fill:'var(--yellow)','font-style':'italic'});
  t.textContent = `cycle shape = ${shapeStr(shape)}`;
  svg.appendChild(t);
  out.textContent = `Frobenius type: ${P.name}\n${P.factorisation}`;
}
function cycleShapeFromPerm(p){
  const n = p.length; const seen = new Array(n).fill(false); const cycs = [];
  for(let i=0;i<n;i++){
    if(seen[i]) continue;
    let j = i, L = 0;
    while(!seen[j]){ seen[j]=true; j=p[j]; L++; }
    cycs.push(L);
  }
  cycs.sort((a,b)=>b-a);
  return cycs;
}
document.querySelectorAll('#w-frob button').forEach(b => b.addEventListener('click', () => {
  document.querySelectorAll('#w-frob button').forEach(x => x.classList.remove('active'));
  b.classList.add('active');
  key = b.getAttribute('data-key');
  render();
}));
render();

